# Rust
target/
**/*.rs.bk

# wasm-pack output — NOT ignored; we ship it so `git clone` + open page works.
# To rebuild: wasm-pack build crates/m2p-wasm --release --target web --out-dir ../../pkg

# Shootout stats files (regenerated by tests). Only java_{100,500,2000}.tsv
# fixtures are committed — anything *_stats.txt / *_run*.txt / *_out.tsv is
# debug noise from re-runs.
/fixtures/*_stats.txt
/fixtures/*_out.tsv
/fixtures/*_run*.txt
/fixtures/rust_*.tsv

